					 In this article 
						 THIS TOPIC APPLIES TO:   SQL Server (starting with 2016) Azure SQL Database Azure SQL Data Warehouse  Parallel Data Warehouse    Returns the Query Store options for this database.   
 Applies to :  SQL Server ( SQL Server 2016 through  SQL Server 2017),  SQL Database. 
 Column name 
 Data type 
 Description 
 desired_state 
 smallint 
 Indicates the desired operation mode of Query Store, explicitly set by user.  0 = OFF   1 = READ_ONLY  2 = READ_WRITE 
 desired_state_desc 
 nvarchar(64) 
 Textual description of the desired operation mode of Query Store: OFF READ_ONLY READ_WRITE 
 actual_state 
 smallint 
 Indic